/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梗係叉燒最好食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWhy not both?<br />\n<br />\n叉燒燒肉飯"},{"pid":"a2e9fc66f84f5e166eb3309cdc0f4ea46be74f9f","tid":355282,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我其實係唔識食的，我覺得世界上最好食既野係燒肉飯。</blockquote><br />\n燒肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你真係唔識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梗係叉燒最好食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前細個我都覺叉燒好食，大個之後反而覺得燒肉好食， 叉燒太濃味，燒肉如果整得好，肥而不利，加埋黃色芥醬，世界級</blockquote><br />\n最緊要係咩呀？<br />\n層皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食燒肉唔食皮架，個個都話我怪"},{"pid":"8ae01310eebbe853047d89410651b018735fc31d","tid":355282,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:27